{"word":"ἀνάκειμαι","slug":"ἀνάκειμαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀνάϰειμαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀνά\">ἀνά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κεῖμαι\">κεῖμαι</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> in older <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Gk.\">Gk.</a> the functional <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀνατίθημι\">ἀνατίθημι</a></el> ‘be laid up / dedicated as an offering’; later = <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κεῖμαι\">κεῖμαι</a></el>, ‘lie down’, <b><i>lie</i> <a href='B:480 5:40'>Mk 5:40</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp> <i>recline</i></b> (at a dinner-table) = <b><i>dine</i> <a href='B:470 9:10'>Mt 9:10</a>; <a href='B:480 16:14'>Mk 16:14</a>;</b> in privileged position <b><a href='B:500 13:23'>J 13:23</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a> ἀναϰείμενος</el> <i>guest:</i> at a wedding <b><a href='B:470 22:10'>Mt 22:10</a>;</b> at an outdoor banquet <b><a href='B:500 6:11'>J 6:11</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνακάμπτω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνακεφαλαιόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}